              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>potten</expan> ist <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> dich <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan> Muffels <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> einr meynt, daz
            er etlich sein hab bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan> der Unrüwin <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> und in <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> gwalt <expan>gefunde<ex>n</ex></expan> hab und hat auch
                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> rechts begert; <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> des
            Muffels armmann wir von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> niht geweisen noch <expan>gewerffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi> Agnetis
